nding computers has always been creation.  So naturally software developer has been a field that has always drawn me in.  Even during high school I remember learning C++ and SDL so I could actually make a game engine, before easily available solutions like Unity and Unreal came into play.\\n\\nToday I find myself always tinkering with the latest techologies and how they can be used together to create powerful tools, systems, and applications.  I hope to add more to this blog/portfolio as I continue to learn\"}]],\"sections\":[[10,0]]}","page":true,"slug":"about","status":"draft","title":"About","updated_at":"2018-01-22T16:49:56.000Z","updated_by":"1","tags":{"0":{"id":"5a661466f98e080d70b4d43f","name":"About","slug":"about","description":null,"parent":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null,"visibility":"public","created_at":"2018-01-22T16:42:14.000Z","updated_at":"2018-01-22T16:49:56.000Z","created_by":"1","updated_by":"1"}},"author_id":"1"}}},"query":{"include":"tags"}},"res":{"_headers":{"x-powered-by":"Express","cache-control":"no-cache, private, no-store, must-revalidate, max-stale=0, post-check=0, pre-check=0","x-cache-invalidate":"/p/aee27269-61a4-4f36-a6ae-779e760f92a6/","content-type":"application/json; charset=utf-8","etag":"W/\"a7e-vUk4NaYqVTIGMWg0vKf0QMuUQR0\"","vary":"Accept-Encoding","content-encoding":"gzip"},"statusCode":200,"responseTime":"95ms"},"msg":"","time":"2018-01-22T16:50:16.978Z","v":0}
